supports asynchronous remote"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"activation over D-Bus, this call may return before the relevant"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"D-Bus traffic has been sent, or any replies have been received. In"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"order to block on such asynchronous activation calls,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] should be called prior to the code, which"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"depends on the result of the action activation. Without flushing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the D-Bus connection, there is no guarantee that the action would"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have been activated.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code which runs in a remote app instance, shows an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"example of a ‘quit’ action being activated on the primary app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"instance over D-Bus. Here [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] is called","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"before "},{"code":"exit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Without "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dbus_connection_flush()"},{"type":"text","text":", the ‘quit’ action"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"may fail to be activated on the primary instance.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["\/\/ call ‘quit’ action on primary instance","g_action_group_activate_action (G_ACTION_GROUP (app), \"quit\", NULL);","","\/\/ make sure the action is activated now","g_dbus_connection_flush (…);","","g_debug (\"Application has been terminated. Exiting.\");","","exit (0);"],"syntax":"c","type":"codeListing"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/actiongro